data.description: Welcome to this gorgeous 5 Bed, 3.5 Bath Colonial nestled at the end of an idyllic, secluded cul-de-sac on a prime, 1.3 acre lot surrounded by mature woodlands in the highly desirable Caves Park neighborhood along the Greenspring Valley Corridor. With its spacious design, set gently in a coveted geographic hub with lush wooded surroundings, and a host of exceptional features, this house is a haven of relaxation and style. The main level has many distinct living areas, but an open flow that allows them all to be interconnected, including a recently renovated kitchen, a spacious living room with exposed beams and stately fireplace with stone hearth, a bedroom/office, a dining room drenched in afternoon light, and a cozy family room with French doors opening to the large sunroom which leads out to the backyard patio and fabulous in-ground pool. The main floor features a mixture of newer hardwood and luxury vinyl flooring. The kitchen was recently renovated and thoughtfully appointed with stainless steel appliances, granite countertops, and a large center island, with a fully renovated half bath nearby. Enjoy hosting company in your sunroom surrounded by private wooded views while preparing hors d'Oeuvres and cocktails in the nearby kitchen, all after a day of enjoying your saltwater heated pool with friends. As you head upstairs, you’ll notice the new (2023) hardwood flooring spread across 4 bedrooms as well as new luxury vinyl plank in all 3 bathrooms. The spacious primary bedroom features a large walk-in closet with windows overlooking the backyard as well as a recently renovated en-suite bathroom with double vanities and shower with newer tile surrounds. The other 2 bathrooms are shared by the other 3 bedrooms. The lower level features entirely new (2023) luxury vinyl flooring, ceiling tiles, and light fixtures. This large basement is a great option for rec room, exercise area, media space, or whatever your heart desires. New (2023) Samsung washer and dryer are located in the basement, which is also equipped with a complete french drain system and sump pump to prevent water intrusion. If outdoor space is what you need, let’s talk about your private backyard. It's a secluded haven enclosed with a fence ready for your flagstone patio hang outs. You also have plenty of parking with your extended driveway and 2 car garage. The entire exterior of the home was also newly painted in late 2023. No expense has been spared in the maintenance of this home. From the roof, siding, to the bathrooms and kitchen. Most listings will say “well maintained, well loved,” however this home is different…so many of the maintenance items have been taken care of for you! New well water pump (2019), new windows (2020), new water heater (2021), new septic tank line (2021), new oil tank (2023). Too many to list! This is the home you've been dreaming of – a perfect blend of modern comforts in a tranquil, peaceful neighborhood, all while being just minutes from everywhere you want to be. Come, make this house your home-sweet-home today!
